<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to Assembl</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; background: #f5f5f5; margin: 0; padding: 20px; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; }
    .header { background: #6366f1; padding: 32px 40px; text-align: center; }
    .header h1 { color: #fff; margin: 0; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; }
    .body { padding: 40px; }
    .body h2 { color: #1a1a1a; margin-top: 0; }
    .body p { color: #4a4a4a; line-height: 1.6; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; background: #6366f1; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; padding: 12px 28px; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; margin: 16px 0; }
    .footer { padding: 24px 40px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; text-align: center; }
    .footer p { color: #999; font-size: 12px; margin: 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to Assembl</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <h2>Hey {{name}}! 👋</h2>
      <p>We're thrilled to have you on board. Assembl is your go-to platform for discovering and attending amazing events.</p>
      <p>Here's what you can do:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Browse and register for events</li>
        <li>Build your profile and connect with attendees</li>
        <li>Track your event history and reviews</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="{{frontendUrl}}/events" class="btn">Explore Events</a>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{year}} Assembl. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
